ă gpt.a+ - Mini-GPT: Multi-Head Transformer in Pure A+
ă First-ever GPT implemented entirely in A+!
ă 8-token vocab, 4-head attention, FFN, layer norm, residuals
ă Trained weights from Python; forward pass + self-test in A+

ă === Model Configuration ===
vocabű8
seqű4
dmű8
nheadsű4
dkű2
dffű16

ă === Helper: Sigmoid ===
sigmoid{x}: {
  Ő 1ß1+*-x
}

  ă === Helper: Softmax (row-wise) ===
softmax{row;n}: {
  ă Find max for numerical stability
  mxűrow[0]
  iű0
  while (i<n) {
    if (row[i]>mx) { mxűrow[i] }
    iűi+1
  }
  ă Compute exp(x - max) and sum (store in temporary array)
  tmpűn Î 0
  smű0.0
  iű0
  while (i<n) {
    eű*row[i]-mx
    tmp[i]űe
    sműsm+e
    iűi+1
  }
  ă Normalize back into row
  iű0
  while (i<n) {
    row[i]űtmp[i]ßsm
    iűi+1
  }
  row
}

